:HELP NAME=STRITMGEN.Incident type Maintenance - Help
:XH3.Incident type Maintenance
:ISCH ROOTS='incident type maintenance'.
Incident type Maintenance

:P.
The incident type maintenance function enables you to maintain incident
types. You can create as many incident type codes as you want.

:P.
Please consult the
:LINK PERFORM='DSPHELP CONINC OMSCONHD'.
Incident concepts
:ELINK.
for more information about incidents.
:EHELP.

