:HELP NAME=OMH01902.General Help For Display 1

:XH3.Display 1 - Work with Incident types

:P.
:LINK PERFORM='DSPHELP STRITM'.
General Information.
:ELINK.

:P.
The :PK.Work with Incident types:EPK. display allows you to change, add or
delete incident types; you can also, via this screen, go to the incident type
action maintenance function.

:P.
Incident types indicate the kind of incident. It is another way of
defining the incident. This attribute is likeliy to be used to
apply a broad shift.
:EHELP.

