:XH3.Option
:P.
These are the list options. The options all act on a
specific HelpDesk code. The following options are available;

:PARML.
:PT.2=Change
:PD.
Use option 2 to change the description of the incident type.
:PT.4=Delete
:PD.
Use option 4 to delete the incident type.
